3. UNDERLYING PUBLIC DATA
================================================================
The underlying water quality measurements are from the U.S. Water
Quality Portal (National Water Quality Monitoring Council — USGS
and EPA), which is public data and remains under its original
terms:
  - https://www.waterqualitydata.us/
  - DOI: https://doi.org/10.5066/P9QRKUVJ

C-HAWQ's compilation, processing, and presentation are the
copyrightable contribution licensed above and do not restrict
independent use of the original public source.

